<p>Photo and video opportunities designed for social sharing multiply launch reach exponentially, with branded backdrops, interactive installations, and shareable moments encouraging attendee documentation and organic promotion. Hashtag campaigns, social wall displays, and real-time content aggregation extend digital presence while reinforcing event energy. For Kenyan product launches, understanding local social media behaviors and platform preferences optimizes shareability design for maximum indigenous relevance.</p>

