<p>Digital overlays for social sharing require optimization for platform specifications—Instagram square formats, Stories vertical orientation, or Facebook landscape preferences—with design variations ensuring optimal presentation across channels. Animated overlays, augmented reality filters, or GIF creation add dynamic elements increasing shareability and platform algorithm favor. Luna Graphics provides template design services ensuring technical compatibility with photo booth software systems and visual excellence supporting brand objectives.</p>

