<p>Color selection impacts visibility and brand communication, with high-contrast combinations (red/white, blue/white, amber) maximizing legibility. RGB capability enables color psychology application—warm tones for appetite stimulation in food retail, cool tones for technology positioning, brand colors for identity consistency. For Nairobi's competitive retail environment, distinctive color strategies differentiate individual stores within crowded commercial districts.</p>

