<p>Lighting design should consider neighborhood context—appropriate brightness respecting residential adjacencies, coordination with surrounding businesses creating cohesive district character, and energy efficiency minimizing operating costs. For premium retail positioning, sophisticated lighting design signals quality investment distinguishing from budget competitors.</p>

