<p>Descriptive language enhances perceived value through appetizing adjectives, origin indication, and preparation method description. Price presentation strategies including removal of currency symbols, strategic rounding, and anchoring with high-priced items influence spending behavior. For Kenyan restaurants, cultural food preferences and local language integration optimize menu effectiveness for specific customer demographics.</p>

