<p>Food photography quality dramatically impacts menu effectiveness, with professional imagery triggering appetite response impossible through text alone. Photography lighting, styling, and post-processing must present food at its most appealing—fresh, abundant, and perfectly prepared. For backlit applications, photography must be optimized for transillumination ensuring appetizing appearance in illuminated presentation.</p>

