<p>Vehicle wraps range from full wraps completely transforming vehicle appearance to partial applications targeting high-visibility areas: full wraps maximizing impact and paint protection; half wraps covering sides and rear; quarter wraps focusing on rear and side panels; spot graphics highlighting specific areas; and window perf enabling rear window graphics maintaining visibility. Coverage selection balances impact objectives with budget constraints.</p>

