<p>Matatu advertising measurement utilizes: route traffic counts and passenger load factors; GPS tracking verifying route compliance; brand awareness studies in covered areas; and response attribution through campaign-specific contact methods. While precise measurement challenges out-of-home media, correlation with sales in served areas indicates effectiveness.</p>

