<p>Waste reduction strategies: avoid single-use items; design for durability and repairability; consider end-of-life recycling programs. Some Kenyan NGOs have shifted to digital alternatives (QR codes linking to resources) reducing physical material needs while maintaining engagement tracking.</p>

