<p>NGO merchandise requires rigorous impact measurement justifying expenditure against mission advancement. Quantitative metrics: distribution numbers, demographic reach, event attendance correlation; qualitative assessment: beneficiary feedback, community perception studies, staff observation. Advanced tracking: QR code engagement analytics, social media hashtag monitoring, pre/post campaign awareness surveys.</p>

