<p>Physical sales environments serve as brand immersion spaces. Sales center design encompasses: architectural model presentation (lighting, interactive elements, scale context); material sample libraries (finishes, fixtures, fittings tactile experience); digital visualization (VR tours, 3D animations, augmented reality overlays); and consultation spaces (privacy for financial discussions, comfort for extended visits). Every element—from flooring to fragrance—contributes to brand perception.</p>

