<p>Setup fees and minimum charges protect providers against unprofitable small jobs. Expect setup fees of KES 500-2,000 per job covering file processing, machine preparation, and material loading. Minimum charges, often equivalent to 30-60 minutes of machine time, ensure viability of small orders. Consolidate multiple projects or combine with other clients' work to amortize fixed costs when possible.</p>

