<p>Engineering support adds value beyond basic cutting. Design for manufacturability (DFM) feedback improves designs for cost-effective production. CAM programming expertise optimizes toolpaths for quality and efficiency. Problem-solving capability addresses unexpected challenges without project abandonment. Assess engineering depth through technical conversation complexity and solution creativity.</p>

